---
permalink: /index.html
bannerImage: cafe_des_minimes.jpg
colorTheme: green
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% from "macros/blogcard.njk" import blogcard %}

{% set metaTitle = "Home" %}
{% set metaDescription = "Portfolio and blog of Jérôme Coupé, belgian designer, developer and teacher based in Brussels." %}
{% set metaImage = "" %}

{% set currentSection = "home" %}

{% block content %}

  <div class="c-section c-section--intro c-section--accent">
    <div class="l-container">

      <div class="c-pageintro">
        <h1 class="c-pageintro__suptitle">Design, Code & Ramblings</h1>
        <p class="c-pageintro__title">
          Like great dishes, I believe websites are made of a few
          <span>simple &amp; well prepared</span> ingredients.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="c-homebanner">
    <div class="c-homebanner__badge">
      {% include("svg/homebadge.svg") %}
    </div>
    <div class="c-homebanner__media">
      <img 
        src="/assets/img/homebanners/800x600/{{ bannerImage }}"
        srcset="/assets/img/homebanners/800x600/{{ bannerImage }} 800w,
                /assets/img/homebanners/1024x768/{{ bannerImage }} 1024w,
                /assets/img/homebanners/1500x1125/{{ bannerImage }} 1500w,
                /assets/img/homebanners/2000x1500/{{ bannerImage }} 2000w"
        sizes="100vw"
        class="c-homebanner__image"
        alt="Café des Minimes, Bruxelles, 2025">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="c-section">
    <div class="l-container">

      <div class="c-section__block">
        <div class="l-split l-split--colgap l-split--half@md">
          <div>
            <h2 class="c-smalltitle">Meet the cook</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
              <p>Webstoemp is the web home of Jérôme Coupé, designer, front-end developer and teacher from Brussels, Belgium. When not coding a website or teaching, chances are I am enjoying a few beers with friends or a gravel ride in the nearby woods.</p>
              <p>Although I work on web apps too, I have a soft spot for building content-oriented websites. To me, Internet will always be a way to share content before being an application runtime.</p>
              <p>
                <a class="c-ctalink" href="#">More about me</a>
              </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="c-section__block">
        <h2 class="c-smalltitle">Latest blogposts</h2>
        {% set items = collections.blogposts | limit(4) %}
        {% for item in items %}
          {% if loop.first %}<ul class="l-grid l-grid--gap l-grid--2cols@sm l-grid--4cols@lg">{% endif %}
            <li>
              {{ blogcard({
                title: item.data.title,
                url: item.url,
                image: item.data.image,
                imageAlt: item.data.imageAlt,
                date: item.date
              }) }}
            </li>
          {% if loop.last %}</ul>{% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        <p class="u-mbs-md"><a class="c-ctalink" href="#">All blogposts</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  
{% endblock %}